#. type: Content of: <sect1><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:11
msgid "Building LFS in Stages"
msgstr "Les étapes de la construction de LFS"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:13
#| msgid ""
#| "LFS is designed to be built in one session.  That is, the instructions "
#| "assume that the system will not be shut down during the process.  That "
#| "does not mean that the system has to be done in one sitting.  The issue "
#| "is that certain procedures have to be re-accomplished after a reboot if "
#| "resuming LFS at different points."
msgid ""
"LFS is designed to be built in one session.  That is, the instructions "
"assume that the system will not be shut down during the process.  This does "
"not mean that the system has to be built in one sitting.  The issue is that "
"certain procedures must be repeated after a reboot when resuming LFS at "
"different points."
msgstr ""
"LFS est conçu pour être construit en une seule session. En d’autres termes, "
"les instructions supposent que le système ne sera pas éteint pendant la "
"construction. Cela ne signifie pas que le système doit être construit d’une "
"traite. Le problème, c'est que certaines procédures devront être relancées "
"après un redémarrage si vous reprenez la construction de LFS à différentes "
"étapes."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:21
msgid "Chapters&nbsp;1&ndash;4"
msgstr "Chapitres&nbsp;1 à 4"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:23
#| msgid ""
#| "These chapters are accomplished on the host system.  When restarting, be "
#| "careful of the following:"
msgid ""
"These chapters run commands on the host system.  When restarting, be certain "
"of one thing:"
msgstr ""
"Ces chapitres exécutent des commandes sur le système hôte. En cas de "
"redémarrage, vérifiez une chose&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:28
#| msgid ""
#| "Procedures done as the <systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem> "
#| "user after Section 2.4 need to have the LFS environment variable set "
#| "<emphasis>FOR THE ROOT USER</emphasis>."
msgid ""
"Procedures performed as the <systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem> "
"user after Section 2.4 must have the LFS environment variable set "
"<emphasis>FOR THE ROOT USER</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Les procédures effectuées en tant qu’utilisateur <systemitem class=\"username"
"\">root</systemitem> après la Section 2.4 ont besoin que la variable "
"d’environnement LFS soit définie <emphasis>POUR L’UTILISATEUR ROOT</"
"emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:37
msgid "Chapters&nbsp;5&ndash;6"
msgstr "Chapitres&nbsp;5&ndash;6"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:41 lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:67
msgid "The /mnt/lfs partition must be mounted."
msgstr "La partition /mnt/lfs doit être montée."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:45
#| msgid ""
#| "These two chapters <emphasis>must</emphasis> be done as user <systemitem "
#| "class=\"username\">lfs</systemitem>.  A <command>su - lfs</command> "
#| "command must be issued before any task in these chapters. If you don't do "
#| "that, you are at risk of installing packages to the host, and potentially "
#| "rendering it unusable."
msgid ""
"These two chapters <emphasis>must</emphasis> be done as user <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">lfs</systemitem>.  A <command>su - lfs</command> command "
"must be issued before performing any task in these chapters. If you don't do "
"that, you are at risk of installing packages to the host, and potentially "
"rendering it unusable."
msgstr ""
"Ces deux chapitres <emphasis>doivent</emphasis> être effectués en tant "
"qu'utilisateur <systemitem class=\"username\">lfs</systemitem>. Vous devez "
"exécuter <command>su - lfs</command> avant d'effectuer quoi que ce soit dans "
"ces chapitres. Si vous ne le faites pas, vous risquez d'installer des "
"paquets sur l'hôte et éventuellement de le rendre inutilisable."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:53
#| msgid ""
#| "The procedures in <xref linkend='ch-tools-generalinstructions'/> are "
#| "critical.  If there is any doubt about installing a package, ensure any "
#| "previously expanded tarballs are removed, then re-extract the package "
#| "files, and complete all the instructions in that section."
msgid ""
"The procedures in <xref linkend='ch-tools-generalinstructions'/> are "
"critical.  If there is any doubt a package has been installed correctly, "
"ensure the previously expanded tarball has been removed, then re-extract the "
"package, and complete all the instructions in that section."
msgstr ""
"Les procédures de <xref linkend='ch-tools-generalinstructions'/> sont "
"cruciales. Si vous avez le moindre doute sur l’installation correcte d’un "
"paquet, assurez-vous d’avoir supprimé toute archive décompressée, extrayez "
"de nouveau les fichiers du paquet et suivez toutes les instructions de cette "
"section."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:63
msgid "Chapters&nbsp;7&ndash;10"
msgstr "Chapitres&nbsp;7&ndash;10"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:71
msgid ""
"A few operations, from <quote>Changing Ownership</quote> to <quote>Entering "
"the Chroot Environment</quote>, must be done as the <systemitem class="
"\"username\">root</systemitem> user, with the LFS environment variable set "
"for the &root; user."
msgstr ""
"Certaines opérations, de <quote>Changer de propriétaire</quote> à "
"<quote>Entrer dans l'environnement chroot</quote> doivent être effectuées en "
"tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem>, avec "
"la variable d'environnement configurée pour l'utilisateur &root;."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:78
#| msgid ""
#| "When entering chroot, the LFS environment variable must be set for "
#| "<systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem>. The LFS variable is not "
#| "used after entering the chroot environment."
msgid ""
"When entering chroot, the LFS environment variable must be set for "
"<systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem>. The LFS variable is not "
"used after the chroot environment has been entered."
msgstr ""
"En entrant dans l’environnement chroot, la variable d’environnement LFS doit "
"être définie pour l’utilisateur <systemitem class=\"username\""
">root</systemitem>. La variable LFS n’est plus utilisée après l'entrée dans "
"l'environnement chroot."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter02/stages.xml:84
msgid ""
"The virtual file systems must be mounted.  This can be done before or after "
"entering chroot by changing to a host virtual terminal and, as <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem>, running the commands in <xref "
"linkend='ch-tools-bindmount'/> and <xref linkend='ch-tools-kernfsmount'/>."
msgstr ""
"Les systèmes de fichiers virtuels doivent être montés. Ceci peut se faire "
"avant ou après être entré dans l’environnement chroot en changeant de "
"terminal dans le système hôte et, en tant que <systemitem class=\"username"
"\">root</systemitem>, en exécutant les commandes de la <xref linkend='ch-"
"tools-bindmount'/> et de la <xref linkend='ch-tools-kernfsmount'/>."
